    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Manages a projection where each entry in source array connects to the corresponding entry (with same index) in dest array. If there is a mismatch in number of entries, the overhang is ignored. If the dest array is a <ref refid="classFieldElement" kindref="compound">FieldElement</ref>, then it uses its internal DataId i2_ to fill in the DataIndex for the dest. The OneToOne matching is assumed to be between DataIndex on e1 and FieldIndex on e2. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
